oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Organic vegetable proteins and oil in feed for organic rainbow trout (Oncorhynchus mykiss)
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Lund, Ivar
Dalsgaard, Johanne
Larsen, Bodil
Jokumsen, Alfred
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Feeding and growth
Recycling, balancing and resource management
Farm nutrient management
Quality and evaluation of inputs
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Fish meal may be partly replaced by a matrix of organic horse bean, pea and rape, and flax seed oil may replace fish oil in diets for organic rainbow trout without compromising growth performance and feed utilization.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Lund, Ivar; Dalsgaard, Johanne; Larsen, Bodil and Jokumsen, Alfred (2010) Organic vegetable proteins and oil in feed for organic rainbow trout (Oncorhynchus mykiss). [Økologiske planteproteiner og olie i foder til økologiske regnbueørreder (Oncorhynchus mykiss).] Poster at: XIV International Symposium on Fish Nutrition and Feeding, Qingdao, China, May 31 - June 4 2010.
